title: Hutchison assembly stands firm against eviction threat
text:
Hutchison assembly stands firm agains... Hutchison assembly stands firm against eviction threat 2 hrs ago Read more: Green Left Weekly 
The community assembly outside the Hutchison terminal at Port Botany is holding firm against a threat by the NSW Port Authority to evict the gathering from the entrance to the facility. There was a similar stand-off at Fishermans Island, Port of Brisbane.   Green Left Weekly.
